DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260706
SUMMARY:[Federal Maine-Related] Atlantic Highly Migratory Species\; Atlant
 ic Bluefin Tuna Fisheries\; Closure of the Angling Category Southern New E
 ngland Area Trophy Fishery for 2026
DESCRIPTION:NMFS closes the Angling category Southern New England area fis
 hery for large medium and giant ("trophy" (i.e.\, measuring 73 inches (185
  centimeters (cm)) curved fork length or greater)) Atlantic bluefin tuna (
 BFT). This action applies to Highly Migratory Species (HMS) Angling and HM
 S Charter/Headboat permitted vessels when fishing recreationally.\nhttps:/
 /www.federalregister.gov/documents/2026/07/06/2026-13630/atlantic-highly-m
 igratory-species-atlantic-bluefin-tuna-fisheries-closure-of-the-angling-ca
 tegory
URL:https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2026/07/06/2026-13630/atlant
 ic-highly-migratory-species-atlantic-bluefin-tuna-fisheries-closure-of-the
 -angling-category
