SUMMARY:[Federal Maine-Related] National Vaccine Injury Compensation Progr
 am\; List of Petitions Received
DESCRIPTION:HRSA is publishing this notice of petitions received under the
  National Vaccine Injury Compensation Program (the Program)\, as required 
 by the Public Health Service (PHS) Act\, as amended. While the Secretary o
 f HHS is named as the respondent in all proceedings brought by the filing 
 of petitions for compensation under the Program\, the United States Court 
 of Federal Claims is charged by statute with responsibility for considerin
 g and acting upon the petitions.\nhttps://www.federalregister.gov/document
 s/2026/06/25/2026-12788/national-vaccine-injury-compensation-program-list-
 of-petitions-received
URL:https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2026/06/25/2026-12788/nation
 al-vaccine-injury-compensation-program-list-of-petitions-received
